1979;;Something Short of Paradise;;American;;David Helpern;;Susan Sarandon, David Steinberg;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Something_Short_of_Paradise;;Madeleine Ross (Susan Sarandon) is a journalist, and her boyfriend, Harris Sloane (David Steinberg), is the owner of an art theatre. Their relationship is on-again/off-again, and when Madeleine meets the French star Jean-Fidel Mileau (Jean-Pierre Aumont) it provokes changes in the way she and Harris feel about each other.